===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Rose (Masters)}}
Rose forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Copperajah}} and {{p|Perrserker}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Copperajah is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing. Rose became a playable sync pair on July 14, 2023.

Rose has made debut for notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. This version of Rose is implied to come from a time when he had not yet caused the [[Darkest Day]].

